As I was sitting here looking for a nice summer vape, tired of the same old stuff, I opened up ATF and this recipe was sitting as the newest entry.&#xD;
We all know the man, the myth, the legend who goes by Id10t. For me, it was automatic to mix it. &#xD;
I whipped up a batch, SNV and came right back to write this review.&#xD;
Perfect timing! . Another well balanced delicious recipe for our mixing enjoyment.  Thanks! You could probably toss a little ws23 in there if you're lookin for a cool summer vape. He doesn't mention it, and there may be a reason for that.
